Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:26.52,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,670)}每次實現時 才會崩壞的 夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:30.98,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,670)}為何 即便如此 我仍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:37.78,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,670)}不斷尋求 繼續奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.90,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,670)}久別重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:41.36,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,670)}「氣氛改變了？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:44.53,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,670)}歲月流逝了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:49.29,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,670)}「還是那個時候快樂」
